Description: Avalon Russett in Laurel, MD between Washington DC and Baltimore, is a short drive to great malls, theaters, parks, the MARC train station, and major military bases and employers. Avalon Russett features 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments with colonial-inspired architecture and fabulous amenities that include white-on-white kitchens, spacious baths, washer/dryer, and cultured marble vanities. Brilliant facilities include a fitness center with cardio theater equipment, free weights and resistance machines, a sports field perfect for football, soccer and other field activities, and free access to Russett Community Center to enjoy tennis, basketball, volleyball courts and more.

Description: Ashley Apartments is a unique garden-style community with panoramic views from each home. Each unit features a huge eat-in kitchen and living room with sliding glass doors to your private balcony. Enjoy our tropical pool setting in the summer, as well as our picnic areas and tot lots for the little ones. Our fitness center is available daily for your convenience. We are centrally located close to shopping, restaurants, schools, 295, and 95 highways. We are also now a part of the Fort Meade Set-a-side Program. Come see why Anne Arundel County is known for having some of the best schools in the metro area! ALL UTILITIES INCLUDED! CALL ABOUT OUR SPECIALS!

Description: Concord Park at Russett is located at in Anne Arundel County at 7903 Orion Circle Laurel, MD 20724. The property is mid-way between Washington, DC and Baltimore, MD with easy access to 295, I-95, Greenbelt and College Park. Concord Park offers distinctive apartment floor plans and options in an elevator access building and is managed by PRP Real Estate Management, a reputable property management company with verified listings on http://www.rentcafe.com. Concord Park offers 1 to 3 bedroom apartments ranging in size from 870 to 1860 sq ft. Each apartment has beautiful finishes including stainless steel appliances, plank flooring, white cabinetry and granite countertops. This rental community is pet friendly. For more details, contact our office at 301-880-1118 or use the online contact form and we will get back to you as soon as possible.

We do not permit American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, Staffordshire Bull Terrier, any mix of the previous breeds, or any other dog or breed deemed aggressive. See management for pet approval and deposit and fee information.

Description: Camden Russett, located in Laurel, MD, offers luxurious living with one, two and three bedroom apartment homes. Our residents enjoy custom features such as spacious walk-in closets, built-in bookshelves, fireplaces, garden tubs, 9-foot ceilings with crown molding, full-size washers and dryers and more. Camden Russett provides many amenities that serve the needs of our residents without them ever leaving the property such as a 24-hour fitness center, a car care center, resort-style pool with sun deck, Russett community walking foot and bike path and outdoor social space with grilling stations. Downtown D.C., Laurel Park, National Harbor, FedEx Field, Arundel Mills Mall, BWI Airport and more are just short trips away with access to I-295 and I-95. We can't wait to welcome you home at Camden Russett! Please note that all floor plan availability is subject to change. Call for details.

Description:
Ready to rent! This spacious end-unit townhouse is conveniently located in the desirable, secure Russett Green neighborhood near great schools and close proximity to Ft. Meade, NSA, Baltimore and DC. The home features a gorgeous updated open floor plan, with separate dining and living areas. Host your guests on the lovely open deck overlooking the backyard and community playground. The first floor has an updated ½ bath with new fixtures, a spacious living room/rec room and a separate laundry suite. The second floor also features a beautiful eat in kitchen with granite countertops, plenty of cabinet space and all stainless steel appliances. The third floor has three spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space, and an updated full bath with custom tiled floor. The master bedroom has it's own master bathroom suite with soaking tub and walk-in shower, as well as "his-and-hers" sinks.
Utilities: Tenant pays for electric and water.
Call or email today to schedule a showing!
(301) 637-7368
leasing@realpropertymetro.com
**No Pets** **No Smoking**
Application Requirements:
-Everyone 18 and older MUST apply
-Under 600 credit score will be denied
-Under 650 may require up to 2 months deposit
-Must gross at least 3x your amount of rent
-Must have good rental history
**security deposit, first month's rent and a signed lease due within 48 hours of approval, unless otherwise agreed upon**
